      "Title": "Plugins.Saneject.Editor.Inspectors.Models.ComponentModel",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Plugins.Saneject.Editor.Inspectors.Models.ComponentModel.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Encapsulates a target component and its inspectable properties for drawing in the custom Saneject inspector.\nThis model reflects on the target object's type to collect all drawable fields and constructs\nPropertyModel instances for each field, handling serialized interfaces, nested types, and\ninjection-aware properties.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Plugins.Saneject.Editor.Inspectors.Models.PropertyModel.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Plugins.Saneject.Editor.Inspectors.Models.PropertyModel.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Plugins.Saneject.Editor.Inspectors.Models.PropertyModel",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Plugins.Saneject.Editor.Inspectors.Models.PropertyModel.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Encapsulates metadata and state for a serializable property in the custom Saneject inspector.\nThis model combines reflection information about a field with its serialized property representation,\nhandling special cases like <xref href=\"Plugins.Saneject.Runtime.Attributes.SerializeInterfaceAttribute\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> fields, nested serializable types, injected fields,\nand read-only properties. It supports hierarchical property structures for nested types and collections.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Plugins.Saneject.Editor.Inspectors.Models.yml",
      "output": {
