      "Title": "Plugins.Saneject.Editor.Inspectors.SanejectInspector",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Plugins.Saneject.Editor.Inspectors.SanejectInspector.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Provides UI drawing and validation logic for the custom Saneject inspector.\nHandles rendering of serialized properties with injection-aware read-only states,\ncustom handling for <xref href=\"Plugins.Saneject.Runtime.Attributes.SerializeInterfaceAttribute\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> fields, nested serializable types, and validation\nto ensure assigned objects implement expected interface types.</p>\n"
    },
