      "Title": "Plugins.Saneject.Runtime.Bindings.Component.ComponentBindingBuilder<TComponent>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Plugins.Saneject.Runtime.Bindings.Component.ComponentBindingBuilder-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Fluent builder for configuring component bindings within a <xref href=\"Plugins.Saneject.Runtime.Scopes.Scope\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.\nAllows specifying how to locate <xref href=\"Plugins.Saneject.Runtime.Bindings.Component\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> instances from the scene- or prefab hierarchy.\nSupports locating from the scope, injection target, custom transforms, scene-wide queries, or explicit instances.\nReturned from binding methods like <code>BindComponent&lt;TComponent&gt;()</code> or <code>BindMultipleComponents&lt;TComponent&gt;()</code>.</p>\n"
    },
