      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Plugins.Saneject.Runtime.Bindings.Component.GlobalComponentBindingBuilder<TComponent>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Plugins.Saneject.Runtime.Bindings.Component.GlobalComponentBindingBuilder-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Builder for configuring global component bindings.\nSame as <xref href=\"Plugins.Saneject.Runtime.Bindings.Component.ComponentBindingBuilder%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>, except this builder doesn't allow qualifiers and <xref href=\"Plugins.Saneject.Runtime.Proxy.RuntimeProxy%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> bindings.\nComponents bound with this builder are added to the declaring <xref href=\"Plugins.Saneject.Runtime.Scopes.Scope\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> and added to the <xref href=\"Plugins.Saneject.Runtime.Scopes.GlobalScope\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> at runtime before any Awake methods execute.</p>\n"
    },
